  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    AddMenu
    This activity gets created when the user clicks on the button Add Menu in the MainActivity page.
    CustomizeMenu
    This activity gets created when the user is in the Schedule Menu and clicks on the button Customize.
    InventoryMenu
    This activity gets created when the user clicks on the button Inventory Menu in the MainActivity page.
    MainActivity
    This class shows the main page which contains the three menu buttons (add, equipment and schedule).
    ScheduleMenu
    This activity gets created when the user clicks on the button Schedule Menu in the MainActivity page.
    TimePickerFragment
    When the time in the schedule page is clicked, this activity gets called and a time picker gets created.
